Welcome to Dizzy Radio, the radio streaming app. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect information about you when you use the Dizzy Radio mobile application (the "App") and its related services. By accessing or using the App, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect

Information You Provide: When you use the App, you may provide us with information, including but not limited to your name, email address, username, password, and any other information you choose to provide.
Automatically Collected Information: We may automatically collect certain information about your device, including your IP address, device type, operating system, unique device identifiers, mobile network information, and information about the way you use the App.
Usage Data: We may collect information about your interactions with the App, including the radio stations you listen to, the duration of your sessions, and your interactions with features of the App.
2. How We Use Your Information

We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including to:

Provide, maintain, and improve the App;
Personalize your experience and deliver customized content;
Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support;
Communicate with you about the App and send you updates and notifications;
Monitor and analyze trends, usage, and activities in connection with the App;
Detect, investigate, and prevent fraudulent or unauthorized activity;
Comply with legal obligations.
3. Sharing of Your Information

We may share your information with third parties for various purposes, including:

With service providers who assist us in operating the App and providing related services;
With third parties for marketing, advertising, or other promotional purposes, with your consent;
In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets;
To comply with legal obligations or protect the rights, property, or safety of Dizzy Radio or others.
4. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

5. Your Choices

You may choose not to provide certain information, but this may limit your ability to use certain features of the App. You can also opt-out of receiving promotional emails from us by following the instructions in those emails.

6. Children's Privacy

The App is not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe that we may have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us.

7. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or change this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the App. Your continued use of the App following the posting of any changes constitutes acceptance of those changes.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [contact@email.com].
